ee9b28","tid":304311,"uid":84212,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:07:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73133c05600610182bc67532583b9dafd8d1bb63","tid":304311,"uid":35911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:08:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>豬低賤 唔當動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係豬智商好高，可以做人類朋友</blockquote><br />\n而且你哋班香港市民住嘅地方仲低賤過隻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁講我哋連動物都不如"},{"pid":"5eabec87f5120ce01bb7e6d1d108ddec3d4c727b","tid":304311,"uid":26274,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:08:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔俾其他人殺豬得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你代表全人類咪係"},{"pid":"850a78ee9d06289c634da39e0b54f54bec80f471","tid":304311,"uid":35911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:09:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔俾其他人殺豬得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你代表全人類咪係</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a391afef9dcaba1e3e8f0b509aa75f406f3c5f4","tid":304311,"uid":59654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:10:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>豬低賤 唔當動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗都係 <br />\nbtw 去過廣西食狗肉 配南乳好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a726ed9add471246b80be87e1d2df55d2b0bc07","tid":304311,"uid":35911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:10:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔俾其他人殺豬得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你代表全人類咪係</blockquote><br />\n但係啲狗撚唔俾人食狗，但係佢哋都食豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b845d933c7c941a07934f36fbb4b2e49a3702f6","tid":304311,"uid":35911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:11:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>豬低賤 唔當動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗都係 <br />\nbtw 去過廣西食狗肉 配南乳好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小心俾人話你殘害動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b402b8a9ea5805b670959f47614e801c5c5654","tid":304311,"uid":84212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:13:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6dbf7240056820e017df259c2d3361e9eb1ff28","tid":304311,"uid":35911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T19:15:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>豬低賤 唔當動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nagger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 狗都係 <br />\nbtw 去過廣西食狗肉 配南乳好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 